<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="27" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="27">
≡ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="de Vriese" authorityYear="1854" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Goodeniaceae" genus="Dampiera" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Dampiera verreauxii" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="27" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="verreauxii">Dampiera verreauxii</taxonomicName>
de Vriese, Natuurk. Verh. Holl. Maatsch. Wetensch. Haarlem ser. 2, 10: 118, t. 20. 1854 ≡ 
<taxonomicName authority="Bentham, 1868" authorityName="Benth" authorityYear="1868" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Goodeniaceae" genus="Verreauxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Verreauxia paniculata" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="27" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="paniculata">Verreauxia paniculata</taxonomicName>
Benth., Fl. Austral. 4: 105. 1868, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="27">nom. illeg., nom. superfl.</emphasis>
≡ 
<taxonomicName authority="Bentham, 1868" authorityName="R. C. Carolin" authorityYear="1980" baseAuthorityName="de Vriese" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Goodeniaceae" genus="Verreauxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Verreauxia verreauxii" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="27" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="verreauxii">Verreauxia verreauxii</taxonomicName>
(de Vriese) Carolin, Telopea 2(1): 75. 1980. Type citation: &quot;Nov. Holl. specimine mihi humanissime oblato cum mutlis aliis plantis Novae Hollandiae, a Celeb. Inventore Verreaux, dum hoc. anno 1850 in nostre urbe degebat. Plurimas etiam alias stirpes ab hoc Naturae Investigore repertas et ad Goodenovieas reletas, vidi in Herb. Musei Horti Parisiensis.&quot;
</paragraph>
